      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note>
<div><a href="http://www.workfront.com/it-demo/">http://www.workfront.com/it-demo/</a> - project management tool (good!)</div>
<div><a href="http://actionspace.com/features/">http://actionspace.com/features/</a></div>
<div><a href="http://2-plan.com/">http://2-plan.com/</a> - (open source, download)</div>
<div><a href="https://www.wrike.com/project-management/">https://www.wrike.com/project-management/</a></div>
<div><a href="https://trello.com/signup">https://trello.com/signup</a></div>
<div><a href="http://www.smartsheet.com/">http://www.smartsheet.com/</a></div>
<div>- trage interface</div>
<div>- sheet per project</div>
<div>- geen client overview</div>
<div>- Resouce overview lijkt niet te werken</div>
<div><a href="https://joepjoepsen.resourceguruapp.com/projects">https://joepjoepsen.resourceguruapp.com/projects</a></div>
<div>- leuke app</div>
<div>- resource management</div>
<div>- geen Gantt chart</div>
<div><a href="http://www.tomsplanner.com/software/project-planning/pricingsignup.aspx">http://www.tomsplanner.com/software/project-planning/pricingsignup.aspx</a></div>
<div>- only Gantt, nothing more</div>
<div><a href="http://projectwizards.net/en/">http://projectwizards.net/en/</a></div>
<div><br/></div>
<div>timewax</div>
<div>timeking</div>
<div><br/></div>
<div>TeamGantt</div>
<div><br/></div>
<div><br/></div>
<div><br/></div>
<div><a href="https://www.appguru.com/welcome/features/">https://www.appguru.com/welcome/features/</a> - Access control for all SAAS apps</div>
<div><br/></div>
<div><a href="https://www.officetimeline.com/">https://www.officetimeline.com/</a> - export timelines to powerpoint</div>
<div><br/></div>
